name: Square Jump!
description: Square Jump! is a simple yet powerful 2D platformer where players run, jump, and overcome obstacles in handcrafted levels. With a built-in level editor, you can create your own platforming challenges by placing platforms, hazards, collectibles, and enemies using an intuitive drag-and-drop interface. Best of all, you can share your levels with other players! Think you can create the hardest level of them all?
